00:20:29,228 --> 00:20:32,228
言ってくれてたので。
...she wanted to sing by Lui-senpai's side one day.

172
00:20:32,228 --> 00:20:35,028
なので今日は、お呼びさせていただきました！
So today, I invited her to join me!

173
00:20:35,028 --> 00:20:37,028
ありがとうございます！
Thank you so much!

174
00:20:37,028 --> 00:20:39,228
いや、めちゃくちゃカッコいい曲を
Wow, we got to sing such a cool song together,

175
00:20:39,228 --> 00:20:42,428
歌わせていただきましたが、皆さんいかがでしたか？
but how did everyone like it?

176
00:20:42,428 --> 00:20:44,228
「ねこたん良かったね」って。
They're saying, "Good for you, Nekotan!"

177
00:20:44,228 --> 00:20:47,228
いや、いいです、もう。ねこたんのことはいいんです。
No, it's fine! Don't worry about Nekotan!

178
00:20:47,228 --> 00:20:48,428
「ねこたん良かったね」って。
"Good for you, Nekotan!"

179
00:20:48,428 --> 00:20:51,528
そんなことより、ルイ先輩、ねこたん何回、今日重大告知もあるし。
More importantly, Lui-senpai! You have some major announcements today...

180
00:20:51,528 --> 00:20:53,228
そうなんです。
That's right.

181
00:20:53,228 --> 00:20:54,628
し、新衣装も。
...and... and a new outfit, right?

182
00:20:54,628 --> 00:20:56,028
新衣装もあるんです。
Yes, I also have a new outfit.

183
00:20:56,028 --> 00:20:57,228
出るんでしたっけ？
Was that coming out?

184
00:20:57,228 --> 00:21:00,728
これね、たくさんね、ここのハッシュタグ、
So, we have this hashtag here,

185
00:21:00,728 --> 00:21:04,228
#鷹嶺ルイ超重大生誕LIVE ってありますので、
#鷹嶺ルイ超重大生誕LIVE...

186
00:21:04,228 --> 00:21:07,728
それでたくさんたくさん、ポストしてくれたら嬉しいなと思うんですけど。
...and I'd be so happy if you could post using it a lot.

187
00:21:07,728 --> 00:21:10,228
今日はたくさん、告知もありますし。
But today we have so many announcements...

188
00:21:10,228 --> 00:21:12,228
そうですよね。
Right.

189
00:21:12,228 --> 00:21:15,228
いや、ねこたん気になるのももちろん、重大告知のデカさも気になるんですけど。
I mean, Nekotan is curious too, but I'm also curious about how big the major announcements are...

190
00:21:15,228 --> 00:21:18,428
新衣装がやっぱりね、気になる。
...but I'm really curious about the new outfit.

191
00:21:18,428 --> 00:21:22,228
やっぱルイ先輩って言えば、こうちょっとダークネスな感じなのかなとか思って。
When I think of Lui-senpai, I wonder if it'll have a dark vibe to it...

192
00:21:22,228 --> 00:21:25,228
ああ、なるほど、なるほど、なるほど。
Ah, I see, I see, I see.

193
00:21:25,228 --> 00:21:26,728
暗い、黒系なのかな、みたいな。
...like a dark or black-themed one.

194
00:21:26,728 --> 00:21:28,228
ああ、なるほどなるほど。そう思いますよね。
Ah, I see. That makes sense.

195
00:21:28,228 --> 00:21:30,228
はい。
Yes.

196
00:21:30,228 --> 00:21:31,428
ま、それもあります。
Well, that is part of it.

197
00:21:31,428 --> 00:21:32,728
おお、それも！
Oh, that too?!

198
00:21:32,728 --> 00:21:33,728
それは、ということは？
Which means...?

199
00:21:33,728 --> 00:21:35,228
最初ね、あの、固定でも書かせていただいたんですけど。
At first, as I wrote in the pinned post as well...

200
00:21:35,228 --> 00:21:39,228
はい。
...yes.

201
00:21:39,228 --> 00:21:40,228
あの、新衣装は最初、サブカラー。
The new outfit starts with a sub-color...

202
00:21:40,228 --> 00:21:44,028
え？
Huh?

203
00:21:44,028 --> 00:21:45,228
で、ちょっと清楚な感じの衣装になっております。
...and it'll be a slightly elegant and pure style.

204
00:21:45,228 --> 00:21:48,428
え？それもあるってこと？他にもあるってこと？
Huh? You have that too? There are others?!

205
00:21:48,428 --> 00:21:52,228
はい。めちゃくちゃ大量にサブを用意しておりますので、最後までね、楽しんで。
Yes. I've prepared a huge variety of sub-options, so look forward to it until the end.

206
00:21:52,228 --> 00:21:56,228
何かすごい騒いでる。
Something's making a huge racket...

207
00:21:56,228 --> 00:21:58,228
おかしい。
How strange.

208
00:21:58,228 --> 00:21:59,428
サブ！
Subs!

209
00:21:59,428 --> 00:22:00,728
うん。もういいや、今日は来てくれてありがとう。
Yeah. Anyway, thank you for coming today.

210
00:22:00,728 --> 00:22:03,028
わかりました。楽屋で応援してます。それでは！
Understood. I'll cheer you on from the dressing room. Well then!

211
00:22:03,028 --> 00:22:06,228
あ、違う違う。そ、そちらは舞踏会会場なんで。
Ah, wait, no. That direction is the ballroom.

212
00:22:06,228 --> 00:22:09,228
え？ダメなんですか？ねこたん。
Huh? Is it off-limits to Nekotan?

213
00:22:09,228 --> 00:22:11,228
ねこたんは呼んでない。招待状もらってないでしょ？
I didn't invite Nekotan. You didn't get an invitation, did you?

214
00:22:11,228 --> 00:22:15,228
もらってないけど。
I didn't, but...

215
00:22:15,228 --> 00:22:17,728
じゃ、すいませんが、楽屋の方に、あちらから。
So, sorry, but the dressing room is that way.

216
00:22:17,728 --> 00:22:20,228
えー！
Eww!

217
00:22:20,228 --> 00:22:21,228
はい、スタッフさんお願いします。
Alright, staff, please assist her.

218
00:22:21,228 --> 00:22:23,728
ルイ先輩、タッチ、タッチ、タッチ。
Lui-senpai, high-five, high-five, high-five.

219
00:22:23,728 --> 00:22:26,228
ありがとう、ありがとう。
Thank you, thank you.

220
00:22:26,228 --> 00:22:27,728
頑張ってください。
Good luck!

221
00:22:27,728 --> 00:22:29,728
ありがとうね、ありがとうね。
Thank you, thank you.

222
00:22:29,728 --> 00:22:31,428
はい。
Yes.

223
00:22:31,428 --> 00:22:32,228
ありがとうね。
Thank you.

224
00:22:32,228 --> 00:22:34,228
ということでねこたんに来ていただきました。
And with that, Nekotan joined us.

225
00:22:34,228 --> 00:22:36,728
はい、新衣装もね、たくさん見せていきますので、最後まで楽しんでいただけたらなと思います。
Yes, I'll be showing you lots of my new outfits, so I hope you enjoy it until the end.

226
00:22:36,728 --> 00:22:41,228
楽屋のねこたんも楽しんでくださいね。
Nekotan in the dressing room, please enjoy it too!

227
00:22:41,228 --> 00:22:44,228
それでは、聴いてください。
And now, please listen...

228
00:22:44,228 --> 00:22:46,228
ジグザグ。
Zig-Zag.

229
00:22:53,228 --> 00:23:00,228
[Song: ZIG-ZAG
Lyrics, Composition, Arrangement: Ayumi Nakamura / Takayuki Yoshimura]

230
00:23:02,428 --> 00:23:04,228
寄せ集めて囁いた
Gathering and whispering...

231
00:23:04,228 --> 00:23:06,228
「とりあえず」はもう飽きたら
If you're already tired of "for now"...

232
00:23:06,228 --> 00:23:08,228
こびりついて離れない
...stuck on and won't leave...

233
00:23:08,228 --> 00:23:10,228
メロディはだらだらだら
...the melody is just rambling on and on.

234
00:23:10,228 --> 00:23:13,728
無味無臭の生活が思い出せないや
I can't even remember this odorless, flavorless life.

235
00:23:13,728 --> 00:23:16,028
忘れたいから歌った
I sang because I wanted to forget...

236
00:23:16,028 --> 00:23:18,428
ばかりだなだらだらだら
...it's just been a drag, on and on.

237
00:23:19,228 --> 00:23:21,028
恨むことも
Resenting...

238
00:23:21,028 --> 00:23:22,628
憎むことも
...and hating...

239
00:23:22,628 --> 00:23:26,728
賢くない故にできなかった
...because I wasn't smart enough, I couldn't do either.

240
00:23:27,428 --> 00:23:30,728
これが君の結末ならば
If this is your ending...

241
00:23:30,728 --> 00:23:34,228
笑ってしまいたい<
...I want to laugh it off.

242
00:23:34,228 --> 00:23:37,728
嘘 嘘 嘘 嘘 嘘
Lies, lies, lies, lies, lies...

243
00:23:37,728 --> 00:23:39,228
うそつき
...you liar.

244
00:23:39,228 --> 00:23:42,428
痛い 痛い 痛い 痛いな 奇跡とかちょっと乗せちゃって
It hurts, hurts, hurts, hurts, adding a bit of a miracle to it.

245
00:23:42,428 --> 00:23:45,728
もう嫌 嫌 嫌 嫌 たちが悪いわね
I've had enough, no, no, no, no, that's malicious, isn't it?

246
00:23:48,228 --> 00:23:51,228
来ない 来ない 来ない 来ないな おかしなとこ全部えぐり取って
It's not coming, not coming, not coming, gouge out all the strange parts.

247
00:23:51,228 --> 00:23:53,228
悪評だって結構
Even a bad reputation is fine,

248
00:23:53,228 --> 00:23:55,428
好きに呼んでいいよ
you can call me whatever you like.

249
00:23:55,428 --> 00:23:57,428
トラウマにバイバイしたいの
I want to say bye-bye to my trauma.

250
00:23:57,428 --> 00:24:00,728
捨てて 捨てて 捨てて 捨てて
Cast it away, cast it away, cast it away.

251
00:24:09,228 --> 00:24:11,228
私 甘え上手になれなかった
I couldn't be good at pampering...

252
00:24:11,228 --> 00:24:13,228
可愛げとかが足りなかった
...and I lacked any charm.

253
00:24:13,228 --> 00:24:15,228
後悔か？
Is it regret?

254
00:24:15,228 --> 00:24:17,028
うるさいよ、もう
Shut up already.

255
00:24:17,228 --> 00:24:19,228
過去は過去だと割り切っちゃえば
If I just accept that the past is the past...

256
00:24:19,228 --> 00:24:21,728
きっといいことあるさとか
...and believe "surely good things will happen"...

257
00:24:21,728 --> 00:24:23,728
これくらい
...this much...

258
00:24:23,728 --> 00:24:26,028
百も承知だ だらだらだら
...I know all too well, going on and on.

259
00:24:26,228 --> 00:24:28,228
願うことも
Wishing...

260
00:24:28,228 --> 00:24:29,728
祈ることも
...and praying...

261
00:24:29,728 --> 00:24:33,728
許されないから黒く染めた
...aren't allowed, so I dyed them black.

262
00:24:34,428 --> 00:24:38,028
元の色も思い出せない
I can't even remember the original color...

263
00:24:38,428 --> 00:24:41,228
狂った運命の
...of this crazy fate's...

264
00:24:41,228 --> 00:24:44,728
糸 糸 糸 糸
...thread, thread, thread, thread.

265
00:24:46,228 --> 00:24:49,228
痛い 痛い 痛い 痛いな 悲劇のヒロイン気取っちゃって保存
It hurts, hurts, hurts, hurts, pretending to be a tragic heroine.

266
00:24:49,228 --> 00:24:52,428
もう嫌 嫌 嫌 嫌 諦めちゃえばいいのに
I've had enough, no, no, no, no, though it'd be easier to just give up.

267
00:24:55,228 --> 00:24:57,228
会いたい 会いたい 会いたい 会いたいな
I want to see you, see you, see you, see you...

268
00:24:57,228 --> 00:24:59,028
深呼吸 ああ こんがらがっちゃって
...deep breath, ah, getting all tangled up.

269
00:24:59,028 --> 00:25:00,728
明日またきっと
Tomorrow, surely again...

270
00:25:01,045 --> 00:25:02,845
壊すけどいいの？
I'm going to break it, is that okay?

271
00:25:02,845 --> 00:25:07,545
トラウマ退治の Death, Death, de, Death!
Death, Death, de, Death to conquer trauma!

272
00:25:33,445 --> 00:25:38,545
夢の中で君と手を繋いでいるの
In my dreams, I am holding hands with you

273
00:25:38,545 --> 00:25:45,845
何も知らないあの頃の二人のままで
Just like we were back then, knowing nothing

274
00:25:45,845 --> 00:25:51,545
でも分かっているよ すぐに覚めてしまうと
But I know that I will wake up soon

275
00:25:51,545 --> 00:25:58,545
それならばいっそ君の手でそっと 殺して
If that's the case, I'd rather you gently... kill me

276
00:25:59,245 --> 00:26:02,845
ほら 今、今、今、今
Look, now, now, now, now

277
00:26:02,845 --> 00:26:05,545
委ねたい、たい、たい、たいな
I want to surrender, -der, -der, -der...

278
00:26:05,545 --> 00:26:08,545
奇跡とかちょっと望んじゃってもいい？
Can I wish for a little bit of a miracle?

279
00:26:08,545 --> 00:26:11,545
いや、いや、いや、いや、いや
No, no, no, no, no

280
00:26:11,545 --> 00:26:14,245
たちが悪いわ らい、らい、らい、らいな
It's so toxic... -lai, -lai, -lai, -laina

281
00:26:14,245 --> 00:26:16,545
おかしなとこ全部えぐりとって
Scoop out all the strange parts

282
00:26:16,545 --> 00:26:18,545
拍手喝采で結構
Applause is perfectly fine

283
00:26:18,545 --> 00:26:20,545
好きに呼んでいいよ
You can call me whatever you like

284
00:26:20,545 --> 00:26:23,045
トラウマにバイバイしたいの
I want to say goodbye to trauma

285
00:26:23,045 --> 00:26:27,045
Death, Death, de, Death, Death, de, Death

286
00:26:53,345 --> 00:26:58,545
世界欺く揺るぎない正義
An unwavering justice that deceives the world

287
00:26:58,545 --> 00:27:04,045
ほどいて真実この手の中
Unraveling the truth into these hands

288
00:27:10,045 --> 00:27:15,045
アイのシナリオ
[Song: Ai no Scenario]

289
00:27:20,045 --> 00:27:25,045
大胆不敵な影が華麗に踊る
A fearless shadow dances gracefully

290
00:27:25,045 --> 00:27:30,545
君が隠してる秘密いつか聞かせてよ
Tell me someday the secret you're hiding

291
00:27:30,545 --> 00:27:36,045
伸ばした手で触れる事は誰もできない
No one can touch you with an outstretched hand

292
00:27:36,045 --> 00:27:41,045
君が隠してる世界僕に見させてよ
Let me see the world you're hiding

293
00:27:41,045 --> 00:27:44,845
揺れる難解な心
A swaying, complex heart

294
00:27:44,845 --> 00:27:50,045
解き明かして奪うその瞳
Those eyes that solve and steal it away

295
00:27:52,045 --> 00:27:56,845
不安がって泣いてたって見つけらんないよ
Even if you're anxious and crying, you won't find it

296
00:27:56,845 --> 00:28:01,045
狙う真実はどこへ消えた
Where has the targeted truth vanished to?

297
00:28:01,045 --> 00:28:06,545
たとえ世界欺く解答（こたえ）だとしても
Even if it's an answer that deceives the world

298
00:28:08,245 --> 00:28:13,545
「信じて」差し出す掌保存
“Trust me,” I say, holding out my palm

299
00:30:13,665 --> 00:30:18,665
たとえ世界を敵に回したとしても
Even if I make the world my enemy,

300
00:30:18,665 --> 00:30:23,665
「信じて」差し出す掌
"Believe in me," the palm I reach out,

301
00:30:24,165 --> 00:30:29,665
決して離さない 答えは届いた
I'll never let go, the answer has arrived,

302
00:30:29,665 --> 00:30:35,165
結んだ運命 この手の中
The tied destiny is in my hands.

303
00:30:35,365 --> 00:30:40,165
繰り返された 後悔だとしても
Even if it is a repeated regret,

304
00:30:45,665 --> 00:30:50,665
決して逃げない 怖くはないから
I'll never run, because I'm not afraid,

305
00:30:54,165 --> 00:30:57,165
抗うんだ
I will resist.

306
00:31:21,165 --> 00:31:24,165
何度も 何度も
Again and again,

307
00:31:24,165 --> 00:31:27,165
走り続けるよ
I will keep on running.

308
00:31:28,165 --> 00:31:29,365
Wake up! 闘志新生
Wake up! A newborn fighting spirit,

309
00:31:29,365 --> 00:31:31,165
Shift up! ギア回して
Shift up! Shift the gears,

310
00:31:31,165 --> 00:31:32,665
Speed up! 限界叩いて
Speed up! Pushing the limits,

311
00:31:32,665 --> 00:31:34,165
U.M.A. NEW WORLD!!

312
00:31:34,165 --> 00:31:35,665
Jump up! 天辺へ
Jump up! To the top,

313
00:31:35,665 --> 00:31:37,165
Turn up! 声合わせて
Turn up! Raise our voices together,

314
00:31:37,165 --> 00:31:38,665
Dream on! 未来繋いで
Dream on! Connect the future,

315
00:31:38,665 --> 00:31:40,165
U.M.A. NEW WORLD!!

316
00:31:40,165 --> 00:31:43,165
最高潮コンディション 闘志ガンガン尖らせていこう
In peak condition, let's fire up our fighting spirit!

317
00:31:43,165 --> 00:31:46,165
栄光のチャンピオン 虎視眈々と狙っていこう
Glancing at the glorious champion, let's keep a vigilant eye!

318
00:31:46,165 --> 00:31:49,165
ハイペースよりマイペース 気合レースに猛集中
My pace over high pace, focus intensely on the spirited race!

319
00:31:49,165 --> 00:31:52,165
駆けるシグナルは限界 ハートに火をつけ U.M.A. Let's go!
The running signal is at its limit, ignite the heart, U.M.A. Let's go!

320
00:31:52,165 --> 00:31:58,165
最高潮アンビション ぶつかり合ってガチ勝負 絶好のチャンスを 全力出して掴んでいこう
Clashing in a serious showdown with peak ambition, let's give it all to seize this perfect chance!

321
00:31:58,665 --> 00:32:01,365
ハイペースよりマイペース 気合レースに猛集中
My pace over high pace, focus intensely on the spirited race!

322
00:32:01,365 --> 00:32:04,665
掛けるウォームアップはセット完了 勝ち上がっていこう
Warm-up is all set, let's rise to the top and win!

323
00:32:06,665 --> 00:32:10,165
友と二人 競い合った 風の中でも
Competing together, even through the wind,

324
00:32:10,165 --> 00:32:13,165
大きな背中追いかけてた 雨の中でも
Chasing after that big back, even through the rain,

325
00:32:13,165 --> 00:32:16,165
何百何千回と 積み重ねてきた
Hundreds and thousands of times we've accumulated,

326
00:32:16,165 --> 00:32:22,665
だからどこまでも遠く どこまでも高く 誰よりも早く 誰よりも強く
So farther than anyone, higher than anyone, faster than anyone, stronger than anyone!

327
00:32:22,965 --> 00:32:25,165
さあ 今
Now, at this moment,

328
00:32:25,165 --> 00:32:28,165
駆け出した思いはもう止まらない
these running feelings can no longer be stopped!

329
00:32:28,165 --> 00:32:31,165
誰にも渡せないゴールまで
Until the goal that I won't hand over to anyone,

330
00:32:31,165 --> 00:32:34,165
弱気な気持ち蹴飛ばして 強く戦う ずっと
kick away the timid feelings, I'll fight strongly forever!

331
00:32:34,165 --> 00:32:37,165
立ち上がって 走り抜け
Stand up and run through!

332
00:32:37,165 --> 00:32:40,165
鳴り出した鼓動はもう収まらない
The heartbeat that started to ring will not settle down!

333
00:32:40,165 --> 00:32:43,165
最後まで全力疾走 レースを駆けて
Sprinting with full power until the end, running through the race,

334
00:32:43,165 --> 00:32:46,165
頂点へと手を伸ばして 限界さえ超えてゆけ
reach out to the top and go beyond even the limits!

335
00:32:46,165 --> 00:32:50,165
伝説を追い越して 勝利へ
Overtake the legend and go towards victory!

336
00:32:50,165 --> 00:32:53,165
友と二人 競い合った あの喜びも
The joy of competing with you,

337
00:32:53,165 --> 00:32:56,165
